<style>
  .product-page {
    max-width: var(--page-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-page {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Gallery — full bleed images stacked */
  .product-page__gallery {
    position: relative;
  }

  .product-page__gallery-images {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .product-page__gallery-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-warm);
  }

  /* Info panel — sticky on desktop */
  .product-page__info {
    padding: 48px 48px 48px 56px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .product-page__info {
      position: sticky;
      top: var(--header-height);
      align-self: start;
      max-height: calc(100vh - var(--header-height));
      overflow-y: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }

    .product-page__info::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-page__info {
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--page-padding);
    }
  }

  /* Title row */
  .product-page__title-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .product-page__title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-page__title {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }

  /* Price */
  .product-page__price {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .product-page__price-from {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  .product-page__price-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .product-page__price-strike {
    font-weight: 400;
    text-decoration: line-through;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  /* Material info */
  .product-page__material {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Size guide — standalone link */
  .product-page__size-guide-standalone {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    transition: opacity var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .product-page__size-guide-standalone:hover {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* Color swatches */
  .product-page__swatches {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .product-page__swatch {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .product-page__swatch:hover,
  .product-page__swatch.is-selected {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .product-page__swatch--silver { background-color: #C0C0C0; }
  .product-page__swatch--gold { background-color: #D4A853; }
  .product-page__swatch--rose { background-color: #B76E79; }

  /* Variant selector — Length */
  .product-page__variant-group {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .product-page__variant-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .product-page__variant-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .product-page__size-guide {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: opacity var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .product-page__size-guide:hover {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .product-page__variant-options {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .product-page__variant-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .product-page__variant-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .product-page__variant-btn.is-selected {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-text);
  }

  .product-page__variant-btn.is-unavailable {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  /* Add to bag row */
  .product-page__add-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .product-page__add-btn {
    flex: 1;
    height: 56px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background-color: var(--color-btn-primary-bg);
    color: var(--color-btn-primary-text);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .product-page__add-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-btn-primary-hover);
  }

  .product-page__add-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .product-page__wishlist-btn {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--color-btn-primary-bg);
    border: none;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .product-page__wishlist-btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-btn-primary-hover);
  }

  .product-page__wishlist-btn svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    stroke: white;
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.5;
  }

  /* Description */
  .product-page__description {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* Feature list */
  .product-page__features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .product-page__feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .product-page__feature-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .product-page__feature-icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    stroke: var(--color-text);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.2;
  }

  .product-page__feature-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Accordions */
  .product-page__accordions {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .accordion__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .accordion__trigger {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 20px 0;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .accordion__icon {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: transform var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .accordion__item.is-open .accordion__icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .accordion__content {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 300ms ease;
  }

  .accordion__content-inner {
    padding: 0 0 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .specs-table { width: 100%; }

  .specs-table__row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .specs-table__label { color: var(--color-text-secondary); }

  /* Reviews section */
  .product-page__reviews {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    padding: 80px var(--page-padding) 60px;
    max-width: var(--page-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .reviews__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .reviews__title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .reviews__summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .reviews__average {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .reviews__summary-right {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .reviews__summary-stars {
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .reviews__summary-count {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  /* Star breakdown bars */
  .reviews__breakdown {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
  }

  .reviews__breakdown-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .reviews__breakdown-label {
    width: 36px;
    text-align: right;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .reviews__breakdown-bar {
    flex: 1;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .reviews__breakdown-fill {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-text);
    transition: width 600ms ease;
  }

  .reviews__breakdown-count {
    width: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* Photo gallery strip */
  .reviews__photos {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .reviews__photos-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .reviews__photos-scroll {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .reviews__photos-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .reviews__photo-thumb {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .reviews__photo-thumb:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Sort & controls bar */
  .reviews__controls {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .reviews__sort {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .reviews__sort-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .reviews__sort-select {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 8px 32px 8px 12px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    appearance: none;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='10' height='6' viewBox='0 0 10 6' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M1 1l4 4 4-4' stroke='%231A1A1A' stroke-width='1.2' fill='none'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: right 12px center;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .reviews__write-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-text);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .reviews__write-btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews__controls {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    .reviews__sort {
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .reviews__write-btn {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  /* Review cards grid */
  .reviews__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .review-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 28px;
  }

  .review-card__top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .review-card__stars {
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-card__date {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .review-card__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .review-card__photo {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .review-card__photo:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-card__footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .review-card__author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .review-card__author {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-card__location {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .review-card__meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .review-card__verified {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .review-card__verified svg {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    stroke: var(--color-text);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 2;
  }

  .review-card__variant {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  /* Show more button */
  .reviews__show-more {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .reviews__show-more-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 14px 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-text);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .reviews__show-more-btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  /* Write a Review Modal */
  .review-modal {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 9999;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .review-modal.is-open {
    display: flex;
  }

  .review-modal__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .review-modal__content {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 520px;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 40px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .review-modal__content {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0 16px;
      padding: 28px 20px;
    }
  }

  .review-modal__close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 4px;
  }

  .review-modal__title {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .review-modal__field {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .review-modal__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .review-modal__input,
  .review-modal__textarea {
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .review-modal__input:focus,
  .review-modal__textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-modal__textarea {
    min-height: 120px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .review-modal__stars-input {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .review-modal__star {
    font-size: 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--color-border);
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) ease;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .review-modal__star.is-active {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-modal__drop-zone {
    border: 2px dashed var(--color-border);
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .review-modal__drop-zone:hover,
  .review-modal__drop-zone.is-dragover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-modal__drop-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .review-modal__drop-text span {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .review-modal__file-input {
    display: none;
  }

  .review-modal__preview {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .review-modal__preview-img {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .review-modal__submit {
    width: 100%;
    height: 48px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--color-btn-primary-bg);
    color: var(--color-btn-primary-text);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--duration-fast) ease;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .review-modal__submit:hover {
    background: var(--color-btn-primary-hover);
  }

  .review-modal__success {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .review-modal__success.is-visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .review-modal__success-icon {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .review-modal__success-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Lightbox */
  .review-lightbox {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 10000;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
  }

  .review-lightbox.is-open {
    display: flex;
  }

  .review-lightbox__close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    font-size: 32px;
    cursor: pointer;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .review-lightbox__img {
    max-width: 90vw;
    max-height: 85vh;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
</style>

<div class="product-page">
  <!-- Gallery — stacked full-bleed images -->
  <div class="product-page__gallery">
    <div class="product-page__gallery-images">
      {%- if product.images.size > 0 -%}
        {%- for image in product.images -%}
          <img class="product-page__gallery-image"
            src="{{ image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ product.title | escape }}{% if forloop.index > 1 %} - Image {{ forloop.index }}{% endif %}"
            {% if forloop.first %}loading="eager"{% else %}loading="lazy"{% endif %}>
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="product-page__gallery-image" style="background: var(--color-bg-warm);"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info panel -->
  <div class="product-page__info">
    <div class="product-page__title-row">
      <h1 class="product-page__title">{{ product.title }}</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="product-page__price" id="product-price">
      {%- if product.price_varies -%}
        <span class="product-page__price-from">From</span>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}
        <span class="product-page__price-strike">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
      <span class="product-page__price-amount">A{{ product.price | money }}</span>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Material line {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-page__material">
      {%- if product.metafields.custom.material != blank -%}
        {{ product.metafields.custom.material }}
      {%- else -%}
        Sterling Silver, Lab Grown Moissanite
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Size Guide link {%- endcomment -%}
    <a href="/pages/size-guide" class="product-page__size-guide-standalone">Size Guide</a>

    {%- comment -%} Color/finish swatches {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- for option in product.options_with_values -%}
      {%- assign opt_down = option.name | downcase -%}
      {%- if opt_down == 'color' or opt_down == 'colour' or opt_down == 'metal' or opt_down == 'finish' or opt_down == 'metal color' or opt_down == 'metal colour' -%}
        <div class="product-page__swatches">
          {%- for value in option.values -%}
            {%- assign val_down = value | downcase -%}
            {%- if val_down contains 'silver' or val_down contains 'white' -%}
              <span class="product-page__swatch product-page__swatch--silver{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-selected{% endif %}" title="{{ value }}" data-value="{{ value }}"></span>
            {%- elsif val_down contains 'gold' or val_down contains 'yellow' -%}
              <span class="product-page__swatch product-page__swatch--gold{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-selected{% endif %}" title="{{ value }}" data-value="{{ value }}"></span>
            {%- elsif val_down contains 'rose' -%}
              <span class="product-page__swatch product-page__swatch--rose{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-selected{% endif %}" title="{{ value }}" data-value="{{ value }}"></span>
            {%- else -%}
              <span class="product-page__swatch{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-selected{% endif %}" title="{{ value }}" data-value="{{ value }}"></span>
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}

    {%- comment -%} Size/Length variants {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- for option in product.options_with_values -%}
      {%- assign opt_down = option.name | downcase -%}
      {%- unless opt_down == 'color' or opt_down == 'colour' or opt_down == 'metal' or opt_down == 'finish' or opt_down == 'metal color' or opt_down == 'metal colour' -%}
        <div class="product-page__variant-group">
          <div class="product-page__variant-header">
            <div class="product-page__variant-label">{{ option.name }}</div>
            {%- if opt_down == 'length' or opt_down == 'size' -%}
              <a href="/pages/size-guide" class="product-page__size-guide">Size Guide</a>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
          <div class="product-page__variant-options" data-option-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}">
            {%- for value in option.values -%}
              <button class="product-page__variant-btn{% if option.selected_value == value %} is-selected{% endif %}"
                data-value="{{ value }}">
                {{ value }}
              </button>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- endunless -%}
    {%- endfor -%}

    {%- comment -%} Add to bag + wishlist {%- endcomment -%}
    <form action="/cart/add" method="post" id="product-form">
      <input type="hidden" name="id" id="variant-id" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}">
      <div class="product-page__add-row">
        <button type="submit" class="product-page__add-btn" id="add-to-cart-btn"
          {% unless product.available %}disabled{% endunless %}>
          {%- if product.available -%}
            Add To Bag
          {%- else -%}
            Sold Out
          {%- endif -%}
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="product-page__wishlist-btn" aria-label="Add to wishlist">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>

    {%- comment -%} Description {%- endcomment -%}
    {%- if product.description != blank -%}
      <div class="product-page__description">
        {{ product.description }}
      </div>
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="product-page__description">
        Handcrafted in sterling silver featuring lab grown moissanite. These gemstones have the same chemical and physical properties as natural ones — and sparkle just as beautifully.
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- comment -%} Feature icons {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-page__features">
      <div class="product-page__feature">
        <div class="product-page__feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="product-page__feature-text">Hypoallergenic</span>
      </div>
      <div class="product-page__feature">
        <div class="product-page__feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="product-page__feature-text">Strong & Highly Durable</span>
      </div>
      <div class="product-page__feature">
        <div class="product-page__feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="product-page__feature-text">Lifetime Warranty Included</span>
      </div>
      <div class="product-page__feature">
        <div class="product-page__feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="product-page__feature-text">Ethically Sourced & Conflict-Free</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Accordions {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-page__accordions">
      <div class="accordion__item">
        <button class="accordion__trigger">
          <span>The Story</span>
          <span class="accordion__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion__content">
          <div class="accordion__content-inner">
            {%- case product.handle -%}
              {%- when 'the-eclat-tennis-bracelet' -%}
                <p>Each stone in the Eclat Tennis Bracelet begins its journey in a state-of-the-art laboratory in Chiang Mai, Thailand, where master gemologists have spent decades perfecting the art of moissanite cultivation. Grown over 60-90 days using a proprietary thermal process, every crystal is cut by hand in a small atelier outside of Antwerp, Belgium — the same city that has shaped the world's finest gems for over five centuries. The sterling silver settings are cast and polished in a family-run workshop in Arezzo, Italy, a region renowned for its silversmithing tradition since the Renaissance. From stone to clasp, the Eclat represents three continents of craftsmanship unified in a single, radiant piece.</p>
              {%- when 'the-lumiere-stud-earrings' -%}
                <p>The Lumiere Stud Earrings are born from a collaboration between our design studio in Sydney and a multigenerational gem-cutting house in Jaipur, India. Each moissanite crystal is cultivated in controlled laboratory conditions before being precision-cut using techniques passed down through four generations of the Sharma family. The sterling silver ear posts and butterfly backs are produced by artisans in Birmingham, England — a city with a 250-year heritage in jewelry manufacturing. Every pair is individually inspected under 10x magnification before earning the Clear Cut hallmark.</p>
              {%- when 'the-eternite-band' -%}
                <p>The Eternite Band draws its soul from the ancient ring-making traditions of Pforzheim, Germany — known as the Gold City for its 250 years of jewelry mastery. Our moissanite stones are cultivated in a cutting-edge facility in Research Triangle Park, North Carolina, where scientists first pioneered silicon carbide crystal growth. Each stone is hand-set into its sterling silver channel by master setters in Valenza, Italy, where artisans have been crafting fine jewelry since the 1800s. The result is a band that feels as timeless as the commitment it represents.</p>
              {%- when 'the-solaire-pendant' -%}
                <p>The Solaire Pendant captures light the way the sun hits the Mediterranean at golden hour. Each center stone is grown in a laboratory in Seoul, South Korea, using advanced chemical vapor deposition — the same technology used in aerospace-grade optics. The faceting is performed by gemologists in Idar-Oberstein, Germany, a town that has been the heart of European gem cutting since the 15th century. The pendant setting and chain are crafted in a small workshop in Porto, Portugal, where metalworkers shape each piece by hand against the backdrop of the Douro River.</p>
              {%- when 'the-trefle-pendant' -%}
                <p>Inspired by the four-leaf clover motifs found in French Art Deco jewelry, the Trefle Pendant is our tribute to Parisian elegance. Each petal of the clover houses a precisely calibrated moissanite stone, grown in a controlled environment in Nagoya, Japan — a city famous for its precision engineering. The intricate open-work setting is produced by artisans in Lyon, France, using investment casting techniques refined over centuries. Every Trefle is hand-finished with a satin polish that gives it a soft, understated glow rather than a mirror shine — because true luxury whispers.</p>
              {%- when 'the-riviere-tennis-chain' -%}
                <p>The Riviere Tennis Chain is our most ambitious piece — a continuous river of light inspired by the grand necklaces of 18th-century European courts. Over 40 individual moissanite stones are cultivated across a 90-day growth cycle in a facility in Zhengzhou, China, where some of the world's most advanced crystal technology resides. Each stone is calibrated to within 0.1mm tolerance before being hand-set in Vicenza, Italy, by artisans who specialise exclusively in tennis-style settings. The articulated links are engineered to drape naturally against the collarbone, creating that unmistakable cascade of brilliance that turns heads from across the room.</p>
              {%- when 'the-picasso-hoop-earrings' -%}
                <p>The Picasso Hoop Earrings are our tribute to bold, artistic expression — because great jewelry, like great art, should make you feel something the moment you see it. Each hoop is set with 2.6 carats of D-colour VVS moissanite, hand-placed by artisans in a family workshop in Arezzo, Italy, where the tradition of circular jewelry design dates back to Etruscan goldsmiths over 2,500 years ago. The stones themselves are cultivated in a precision laboratory in Busan, South Korea, grown slowly over 75 days to achieve flawless clarity. The sterling silver hoops are cast and plated in a small atelier in Taxco, Mexico — a town synonymous with silver craftsmanship since the 1500s.</p>
              {%- when 'the-quatre-stud-earrings' -%}
                <p>The Quatré Stud Earrings take their name from the French word for four — a nod to the perfectly symmetrical quartet of stones at their centre. Each moissanite crystal is grown over 60 days in a precision laboratory in Wuxi, China, where engineers have pioneered some of the world's most advanced crystal growth technology. The stones are then sent to a third-generation gem-cutting workshop in Surat, India — a city responsible for shaping over 90% of the world's diamonds — where each is faceted to exacting round-brilliant specifications. The sterling silver cluster settings are cast and hand-finished in a small workshop in Córdoba, Spain, a city whose silversmiths have been practising their craft since the Moorish era. Four stones, three continents, one unmistakable sparkle.</p>
              {%- else -%}
                <p>Every Clear Cut piece begins with responsibly cultivated moissanite — grown in advanced laboratories that replicate the extreme conditions found deep within the earth. Our stones are cut and polished by master gemologists, then set by hand in sterling silver by skilled artisans. From laboratory to your jewelry box, each step is guided by our commitment to exceptional quality, ethical sourcing, and timeless design.</p>
            {%- endcase -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion__item">
        <button class="accordion__trigger">
          <span>Shipping & Returns</span>
          <span class="accordion__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion__content">
          <div class="accordion__content-inner">
            <p>Free shipping on all Australian orders over $200. Standard delivery: 8-14 business days with full tracking provided via Australia Post.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:12px;">30-day return window from date of delivery. Items must be unworn, undamaged, and in original packaging. Free return shipping within Australia. Refunds are processed within 5 business days of receiving the returned item.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion__item">
        <button class="accordion__trigger">
          <span>Care Guide</span>
          <span class="accordion__icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion__content">
          <div class="accordion__content-inner">
            {%- assign handle_down = product.handle -%}
            {%- if handle_down contains 'earring' or handle_down contains 'hoop' or handle_down contains 'lumiere' or handle_down contains 'picasso' -%}
              <p>Remove earrings before showering, swimming, or exercising. Clean gently with warm soapy water and a soft cloth — avoid submerging the posts. Pat dry thoroughly. Store in the provided jewelry box with earring backs secured to prevent loss. Avoid contact with perfume, hairspray, and cosmetics.</p>
            {%- elsif handle_down contains 'band' or handle_down contains 'eternite' -%}
              <p>Remove your ring before washing hands, showering, or applying lotions. Clean with warm soapy water and a soft-bristled brush to reach between the stones. Dry with a lint-free cloth. Avoid wearing during heavy lifting or manual work to protect the channel setting. Store separately in the provided ring slot to avoid scratching other pieces.</p>
            {%- elsif handle_down contains 'bracelet' or handle_down contains 'eclat' -%}
              <p>Remove your bracelet before sleeping, showering, or exercising. Clean with warm soapy water and a soft brush, paying attention to the links and clasp mechanism. Dry thoroughly with a soft cloth. Store laid flat in the provided jewelry box to prevent kinking. Avoid contact with harsh chemicals, chlorine, and abrasive surfaces.</p>
            {%- elsif handle_down contains 'pendant' or handle_down contains 'necklace' or handle_down contains 'chain' or handle_down contains 'solaire' or handle_down contains 'trefle' or handle_down contains 'riviere' -%}
              <p>Remove your necklace before sleeping, showering, or applying perfume. Clean the chain and pendant separately using warm soapy water and a soft cloth. Dry thoroughly before storing. Hang or lay flat in the provided jewelry box to prevent tangling. For tennis chains, avoid folding or bending the links — always store laid straight.</p>
            {%- else -%}
              <p>Clean with warm soapy water and a soft brush. Avoid harsh chemicals, chlorine, and abrasive surfaces. Store in the provided jewelry box when not wearing. Remove before showering, swimming, or exercising to maintain the finish.</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Reviews Section -->
<section class="product-page__reviews reveal" id="reviews-section" data-handle="{{ product.handle }}">
